{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1067b","heading":"Grant recipient selection","label":"1067b Grant recipient selection","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/ch28/schIII/ptE/spt1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1067b","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was formerly classified to prior to renumbering by .section 1135b–1 of this titlePub. L. 105–244","Prior ProvisionsA prior was renumbered section 392 and is classified to .section 352 of Pub. L. 89–329section 1068a of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Establishment of criteria","label":"a Establishment of criteria","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067b/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1067b%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Grants under this subpart shall be awarded on the basis of criteria established by the Secretary by regulations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Priorities to be given in criteria","label":"b Priorities to be given in criteria","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067b/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1067b%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In establishing criteria under subsection (a), the Secretary shall give priority to applicants which have not previously received funding from the Minority Institutions Science Improvement Program and to previous grantees with a proven record of success, as well as to applications that contribute to achieving balance among projects with respect to geographic region, academic discipline, and project type.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]